[0m[48;2;40;67;43m[39m+    154[0m:[39m[48;2;24;38;30m [38;2;235;203;139m**[38;2;235;203;139mSuggested fix:[38;2;235;203;139m**[38;2;192;197;206m Add a note: "If your EHR/FHIR server is external to your VPC, Lambda needs a NAT Gateway or the EHR's PrivateLink endpoint for egress. If internal, ensure VPC peering or transit gateway routes are configured. PHI traverses this connection, so TLS is mandatory and mutual TLS (mTLS) is recommended for external EHR APIs."[K
